<text xml:lang="ta" type="edition">
  <body>
    <div rend="parallel">
      <lg xml:id="TCV97">
<l>veyyavāḻi caṅkutaṇṭu villumvāḷu mēntucīrk</l>
<l>kaiyaceyya pōtiṉmātu cērumārpa nātaṉē</l>
<l>yaiyilāya vākkainōya ṟuttuvantu niṉṉaṭain</l>
<l>tuyvatōru pāyamnī yeṉakkunalka vēṇṭumē.</l>
      </lg>
      <lg xml:lang="en">
<l>O [Lord] with excellent hands that hold a fierce discus, conch, staff, bow, and sword!</l>
<l>O You whose chest the Lady on the red lotus joins! O Lord!</l>
<l>You should bestow upon me the means to be saved, coming and reaching You</l>
<l>[after] severing the pain that is the body made of phlegm!</l>
      </lg>
    </div>
  </body>
